 465:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   *           - PWR_SMPS_2V5_SUPPLIES_EXT
 466:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   *
 467:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   * @note   The function modifies the PWR->CR3 register to enable or disable specific
 468:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   *         power supply modes and waits until the voltage level flag is set, indicating
 469:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   *         that the power supply configuration is stable.
 470:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   *
 471:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   * @param  None
 472:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   * @retval None
 473:Core/Src/system_stm32h7xx.c ****   */
